data.description: Charming Tiny Home on a large lot. The home is very functional w/ a spacious living room, built in shelves & a loft to access storage.  The charming eat-in kitchen has a vintage sink that dates back to the 1900's! Use the additional space as an office or spread out & have a larger dining area.  Additional storage or room is located in loft above kitchen. The bathroom is tuck behind a pocket door.   The bedroom has a full size closet.  This cozy cabin has been built w/ efficiency in mind. Covered Patio to enjoy the views!  Lots of space to park an RV's & your toys! Perfect for the minimalist or a weekend get away the possibilities are limitless.
